212 6. Notwithstanding any other provision of this
213 section, any covered voter as defined in section 115.902 or
214 persons who have declared themselves to be permanently
215 disabled pursuant to section 115.284, otherwise entitled to
216 vote, shall not be required to obtain a notary seal or
